text: "Nothin' at All" is a 1986 song by Heart. It is the fourth single from their eighth studio album Heart. It went to number 10 in the United States, number 87 in Australia, number 38 in the United Kingdom, number 18 in Ireland and number 29 in Canada. ==References== Category:1986 songs Category:Power pop songs Category:Heart (band) songs
